HSBC’s Peter Wong Says Hong Kong Inflation Continues to Rise

-- B y   S t a n l e y   J a m e s
-- 
2011-09-19T03:33:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/hsbc-s-peter-wong-says-hong-kong-inflation-continues-to-rise.html
Inflation is continuing to rise in
Hong Kong,  Peter Wong , the bank’s Asia Pacific chief
executiveofficer, said in an interview broadcast on NOW TV
today.  The city’s home market “won’t be too bad” in the medium
to long term, Wong said. HSBC has increased mortgage rates
because of rising capital costs, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stanley James at 
 sjames8@bloomberg.net  